description: Empress Royalty Corp. acquires royalty and streaming interests in precious metal mines and mining projects. The company has a portfolio of 17 precious metals royalties in Canada. It has net smelter return royalty interests in the Pinos Royalty and McLeroy-Pinos Royalty in the Pinos gold-silver project in Mexico. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is headquartered in White Rock, Canada.
